data.description: Don't miss out on this beautiful property on Power Dam Rd, across from the beautiful Auglaize River! This 3 bed, 2 full bath home has two separate living spaces, with the living room opening up to the dining room/kitchen. And don't forget the attached 2.5 car garage! Updates include a brand new HVAC system (2022), new windows and doors throughout the home (2021-2022), updated bathrooms (2021), and a new above ground pool! You will love this peaceful setting on a nearly half acre lot. Schedule your showing today!
